https://cal.com/christopher-wrgldt/topher-ai-demo-call

christopher va a ver tu reserva y te contactará. ¡hablamos pronto! 🎯`; } else { leadSms = `hey ${first} — great chatting just now! sending the booking link so you can lock in a time:

https://cal.com/christopher-wrgldt/topher-ai-demo-call

chris will see your booking and reach out. talk soon 🎯`; }
return [{ json: { ...d, alertText, leadSms } }];

